    </div>
    <div class="pt-4">
        <label for="agreement" class="block text-[#EBF4E9] mb-1 flex items-center space-x-2">
          <input type="checkbox" id="agreement" class="form-checkbox text-[#6A9273]" required>
          <span>Jeg er enig med Let's Do It, Worlds <a href="https://www.digitalcleanupday.org/terms-conditions" target="_blank">vilk친r og betingelser</a></span>
